'''迈克尔·杰克逊音乐视频先锋奖'''（{{Lang|en|Michael Jackson Video Vanguard Award}}），又称为'''音乐视频先锋奖'''、'''终身成就奖'''，成立于1984年的[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]。它由[[音樂電視網|音樂電視網]]推出的，是一份给予对[[MV|MV]]历史有重大影响力的[[音乐人|音乐人]]的奖项。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rihanna Redefines Sporty Chic at VMAs Rehearsal|url=https://www.instyle.com/celebrity/rihanna-redefines-sporty-chic-vma-rehearsal|date=2016-08-28|last=Rabideau|first=Camryn|website=[[InStyle|InStyle]]|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407114035/https://www.instyle.com/celebrity/rihanna-redefines-sporty-chic-vma-rehearsal|archive-date=2020-04-07|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet 'Dr. Luke,' the Man Behind Britney Spears' Award-Winning 'Till the World Ends'|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/man-britneys-award-winning-till-world-ends/story?id=14405542|date=2011-08-30|last=Baker|first=Steven|publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|last2=Effron|first2=Lauren|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326004357/https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/man-britneys-award-winning-till-world-ends/story?id=14405542|archive-date=2020-03-26|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Pink: 2017 VMAs Video Vanguard Award Honoree|url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/news/pink-receive-2017-mtv-vmas-video-vanguard-award|date=2017-08-15|last=Fabian|first=Renée|publisher=[[Grammy_Awards|Grammy Awards]]|access-date=2020-04-08|archive-date=2021-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719121354/https://www.grammy.com/grammys/news/pink-receive-2017-mtv-vmas-video-vanguard-award|dead-url=no}}</ref>作为颁奖典礼的特别奖项，奖杯是镀金的“月人”，而不是其他[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]的银牌。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A Look Back At The Winners Of The MTV VMAs Video Vanguard Award|url=https://www.elitedaily.com/entertainment/celebrity/winners-mtv-vmas-video-vanguard/2026704|date=2017-07-26|last=Wandel|first=Becky|website=[[Elite_Daily|Elite Daily]]|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408022347/https://www.elitedaily.com/entertainment/celebrity/winners-mtv-vmas-video-vanguard/2026704|archive-date=2020-04-08|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>

该奖于1991年开始改名为迈克尔·杰克逊音乐视频先锋奖，名称来自美国著名男歌手[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]。[[邦喬飛|邦喬飛]]和{{link-en|韦恩·伊舍姆|Wayne Isham}}是第一批更名后获奖的艺人。同年晚些时候，在MTV十周年纪念短片中，麦当娜回应道：“我从来没有让你（[[MTV|MTV]]）用我的名字来命名一个奖项，是吗？”。<ref>{{Cite web|title='MTV 10': A Star-Studded Self-Tribute|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1991-11-29-ca-67-story.html|date=1991-11-29|last=Willman|first=Chris|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408020809/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1991-11-29-ca-67-story.html|archive-date=2020-04-08|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>1992年[[枪与玫瑰|枪与玫瑰]]也在获奖感言中称：“这与迈克尔·杰克逊无关，谢谢”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Awards Show Proves MTV's Clout|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1992-09-10-9203220677-story.html|date=1992-09-10|last=Caro|first=Mark|website=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408020809/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1992-09-10-9203220677-story.html|archive-date=2020-04-08|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>迈克尔·杰克逊音乐视频先锋奖在2001年后暂停颁发。2003年[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]的终身成就奖颁给了[[杜蘭杜蘭|杜蘭杜蘭]]，2006年的先锋录影带奖颁给了导演{{link-en|海普·威廉姆斯|Hype Williams}}。迈克尔·杰克逊去世后，该奖项于2011年重新以他的名字颁发。<ref name="auto2">{{Cite web|title=Michael Jackson's Video Vanguard Award, In MJ's Top MTV Moments|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1614838/michael-jacksons-video-vanguard-award-in-mjs-top-mtv-moments/|date=2009-06-26|last=Anderson|first=Kyle|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150102031207/http://www.mtv.com/news/1614838/michael-jacksons-video-vanguard-award-in-mjs-top-mtv-moments/|archive-date=2015-01-02|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>在纪录片《[[离开梦幻岛|离开梦幻岛]]》上映后，这个名字再次引发了争议，该纪录片讲述的是杰克逊涉嫌性侵儿童的故事。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Michael Jackson's name removed from MTV's Video Vanguard Award|url=https://gulfnews.com/entertainment/hollywood/michael-jacksons-name-removed-from-mtvs-video-vanguard-award-1.1567090834985|date=2019-08-29|website=[[Gulf_News|Gulf News]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408022347/https://gulfnews.com/entertainment/hollywood/michael-jacksons-name-removed-from-mtvs-video-vanguard-award-1.1567090834985|archive-date=2020-04-08|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Michael Jackson Video Vanguard Award Teaches MTV the Risks of Naming an Award After a Celebrity: Analysis|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/awards/8528895/michael-jackson-video-vanguard-mtv-analysis|date=2019-09-03|last=Grein|first=Paul|website=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408034114/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/awards/8528895/michael-jackson-video-vanguard-mtv-analysis|archive-date=2020-04-08|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=It's Time for MTV to Rename the Michael Jackson Video Vanguard Award|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/a35z55/its-time-for-mtv-to-rename-the-michael-jackson-video-vanguard-award|date=2019-08-15|last=Corry|first=Kristin|website=[[Vice_(magazine)|Vice]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330213921/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/a35z55/its-time-for-mtv-to-rename-the-michael-jackson-video-vanguard-award|archive-date=2020-03-30|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>

